milestones.description: Kevin Arnott and Ali Shah's 81-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 42 between Paterson and Jack Heron
Dave Houghton and Andy Pycroft's 59-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 30 between Jack Heron and Dave Houghton
Iain Butchart has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (10) for ZIM, going past Kevin Curran
This is the lowest match aggregate (455) involving teams New Zealand & Zimbabwe in ODIs
